    "summary": "<p>Casticle的第三期以硅谷医疗检测公司Theranos和创始人Elizabeth Holmes为主题，推荐了三期相关播客，参考了如下相关文章：</p>\n\n<p>推荐一：Inside Theranos’ Final Days, by Inside the Hive with Nick Bilton</p>\n\n<ol>\n<li>推荐集Inside Theranos’ Final Days的 <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/cn/podcast/breaking-inside-theranos-final-days/id1232383877?i=1000430284921&amp;l=en&amp;mt=2\" rel=\"nofollow\">收听链接</a> ，该播客更早一集讲Elizabeth Holmes的单集播客 <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/cn/podcast/sociopathic-tendencies-inside-elizabeth-holmes-colossal/id1232383877?i=1000413271745&amp;l=en&amp;mt=2\" rel=\"nofollow\">收听链接</a> </li>\n<li>主播兼著名评论人Nick Bilton撰写的同话题 <a href=\"https://www.vanityfair.com/news/2019/02/inside-elizabeth-holmess-final-months-at-theranos\" rel=\"nofollow\">报道</a> ，可以当做推荐集内容的文字版补充；同期，Nick Bilton还写了一篇与Elizabeth Holmes的 <a href=\"https://www.vanityfair.com/news/2019/02/as-theranos-burned-elizabeth-holmes-was-partyingat-burning-man#%7Eo\" rel=\"nofollow\">文章</a> ，内容与推荐集内容有部分重叠，可参考阅读</li>\n<li>文章「超级富豪的末日准备」：英文版详见 <a href=\"https://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2017/01/30/doomsday-prep-for-the-super-rich\" rel=\"nofollow\">New Yorker</a> ，中文翻译版详见 <a href=\"https://www.onespiece.com/blog/584ae1609f1\" rel=\"nofollow\">ONES Piece</a> </li>\n<li>在无数篇谈论Elizabeth声音的文章中，BuzzFeed <a href=\"https://www.buzzfeed.com/jonmichaelpoff/who-is-elizabeth-holmes\" rel=\"nofollow\">这一篇</a> 「混编」19条推文，好似一幅tweet-pastiche，非常新颖，值得阅读；</li>\n<li>纽约时报整理的Theranos事件 <a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2016/07/09/business/theranos-elizabeth-holmes-timeline.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">故事线</a> </li>\n</ol>\n\n<p>推荐二：Elizabeth Holmes, by The Academy of Achievement</p>\n\n<ol>\n<li> 推荐集Elizabeth Holmes在2014年受邀做的7分钟演讲收听 <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/cn/podcast/elizabeth-holmes-audio/id991114681?i=1000341103544&amp;l=en&amp;mt=2\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a> （直接点击链接如无法收听，请在iTunes中搜索Elizabeth Holmes，点击封面中包含the Academy of Achievement字样的单集播客即可），备用演讲视频 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5tEeSHy1x98\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a> （需科学冲浪）；</li>\n<li>Elizabeth 2014为Ted Med做的 <a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/av40065155?from=search&amp;seid=880334606568521025\" rel=\"nofollow\">演讲</a> （此处再次向UP主致谢）</li>\n<li>Quora上网友的 <a href=\"https://www.quora.com/Does-the-low-pitched-voice-of-Elizabeth-Holmes-CEO-of-Theranos-shows-confidence-in-her-words\" rel=\"nofollow\">讨论</a> ：Elizabeth的低沉声音是否能帮她展示出更多自信？</li>\n<li>依然有关Elizabeth声音的 <a href=\"https://www.thecut.com/2019/03/why-did-elizabeth-holmes-use-a-fake-deep-voice.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">参考阅读</a> ，讨论为什么Elizabeth要用假嗓子装男中音</li>\n<li>推荐美剧Valley of the Boom的 <a href=\"https://movie.douban.com/subject/30399030/\" rel=\"nofollow\">豆瓣页面</a> 以及英文 <a href=\"https://www.streamingmedia.com/Articles/Editorial/Featured-Articles/Pixelon-The-True-Story-of-Streaming-Videos-Greatest-Fraud-129289.aspx\" rel=\"nofollow\">影评</a> 一篇（着重描写Michael Fenne）</li>\n<li>2000年，卫报有关Pixelon的 <a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/theguardian/2000/jul/05/features11.g2\" rel=\"nofollow\">报道</a> ，标题是Michael Fenne的「霸气」宣言：「God has blessed me with a unique ability to defy reality」</li>\n</ol>\n\n<p>推荐三：A Taxonomy of Scammers, by Call Your Girlfriend</p>\n\n<ol>\n<li>推荐集的收听<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/cn/podcast/a-taxonomy-of-scammers/id881487725?i=1000413277006&amp;l=en&amp;mt=2\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a> ，推荐集的<a href=\"https://www.callyourgirlfriend.com/episodes#/a-taxonomy-of-scammers\" rel=\"nofollow\">节目备注</a>（即详细的骗子类别大盘点），强烈推荐点击查看详情；</li>\n<li>两篇有关好莱坞巨星Gwyneth Paltrow养生创业项目的文章：一篇来自 <a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2018/07/25/magazine/big-business-gwyneth-paltrow-wellness.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">纽约时报</a> ，另一篇来自 <a href=\"https://www.washingtonpost.com/lifestyle/style/go-ahead-and-hate-goop-gwyneth-paltrow-is-having-the-last-laugh/2018/06/12/edc7c90c-6d86-11e8-bf86-a2351b5ece99_story.html?noredirect=on&amp;utm_term=.98f5f2cddb07\" rel=\"nofollow\">华盛顿邮报</a> ；</li>\n<li>纽约时报的 <a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2019/02/12/style/liars-catfishing-deception.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">文章</a> ：「为什么我们这么喜欢骗子？」</li>\n<li>节目结尾推荐的出自BuzzFeed News的 <a href=\"https://www.buzzfeednews.com/article/alisonwillmore/elizabeth-holmes-theranos-inventor-scammer\" rel=\"nofollow\">文章</a> ，综合剖析了Theranos/Elizabeth Holmes骗局对我们的影响</li>\n</ol>\n\n<p>背景信息补充</p>\n\n<ol>\n<li>John Carreyrou关于Theranos和Elizabeth Holmes的著作 <a href=\"https://www.amazon.cn/dp/152473165X/ref=sr_1_1?__mk_zh_CN=%E4%BA%9A%E9%A9%AC%E9%80%8A%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99&amp;keywords=bad+blood&amp;qid=1553271515&amp;s=gateway&amp;sr=8-1\" rel=\"nofollow\">「Bad Blood」</a> </li>\n<li>ABC出品的播客节目 <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/cn/podcast/the-dropout/id1449500734?l=en&amp;mt=2\" rel=\"nofollow\">The Dropout</a> </li>\n<li>中文媒体对Theranos的报道文章： <a href=\"https://36kr.com/p/5152041.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">36氪</a> ， <a href=\"https://www.ifanr.com/653665\" rel=\"nofollow\">爱范儿</a> ， <a href=\"https://www.qdaily.com/articles/51147.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">好奇心日报</a> </li>\n</ol>\n\n<p>我们十分推荐大家使用通用的播客app收听Casticle和我们推荐的英文节目，推荐使用iOS自带的播客客户端、Overcast、Pocket Casts、Castro和Stitcher等app订阅Casticle~</p>\n\n<p>我们也非常期待收获你的反馈~！如果有任何问题、建议或意见，欢迎你写邮件至<a href=\"mailto:casticlefm@gmail.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">casticlefm@gmail.com</a>与我们联系，或者私信微博账号Casticle。发布播客之余，我们还会不定期在微博及instagram（casticle.fm）上分享一些关于播客的简短讯息与想法，欢迎你随意关注：）</p>",
